dct_description_sm: This polygon data layer represeents minor civil divisions for the state of Wisconsin in 1995. The dataset was originally published by the United States Census Bureau and then processed by the Legislative Technology Services Bureau in 1999.[This data layer is a polygon shapefile of the 1995 minor civil divisions the county, derived from the 1995 TIGER Line Files. It is referenced to the Wisconsin Transverse Mercator (WTM) projection system, North American Datum 1983 with the 1991 adjustment (NAD83/91).]
